# 🤖 AI Chatbot Web App

A full-stack AI-powered chatbot application built using **React (Vite)** and **Spring Boot**, featuring authentication, protected routes, and real-time interaction.

---

## 🚀 Live Demo

🌐 Frontend: https://chatbot-frontend-green-phi.vercel.app/

---

## 📌 Features

* 🔐 User Authentication (Login / Signup)
* 📧 OTP Verification
* 🔑 Forgot & Reset Password
* 🧠 AI Chat Interface
* 📊 Protected Dashboard
* 🌍 Deployed Frontend (Vercel)
* 🖥️ Desktop App (via Nativefier)
* 📱 Mobile-ready (Capacitor / PWA ready)

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

### Frontend

* React (Vite)
* React Router
* CSS

### Backend

* Spring Boot
* JWT Authentication
* REST APIs

### Deployment

* Vercel (Frontend)
* (Backend deployment pending / configurable)

### Desktop

* Electron (via Nativefier)

---

