## ⚙️ Installation & Setup

### 1️⃣ Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/chatbot-frontend.git
cd chatbot-frontend
```

---

### 2️⃣ Install Dependencies

```bash
npm install
```

---

### 3️⃣ Run Development Server

```bash
npm run dev
```

---

### 4️⃣ Build for Production

```bash
npm run build
```

---

## 🌐 Deployment (Vercel)

This project is deployed using **Vercel**.

### Important Config (`vercel.json`)

```json
{
  "rewrites": [
    {
      "source": "/(.*)",
      "destination": "/index.html"
    }
  ]
}
```

👉 Required for React Router (SPA routing fix)

---

## 🖥️ Desktop App (Nativefier)

Convert deployed app into desktop app:

```bash
nativefier https://chatbot-frontend-green-phi.vercel.app \
  --name "AI Bot" \
  --icon icon.ico
```

---

## 📱 Mobile App (Optional)

### Option 1: PWA

* Add to Home Screen (no install needed)

### Option 2: Capacitor

```bash
npm install @capacitor/core @capacitor/cli
npx cap init
npm run build
npx cap add android
npx cap open android
```

---

## 🔐 Authentication Flow

* User Signup → OTP Verification
* Login → JWT Token stored
* Protected Routes using `ProtectedRoute`
* Dashboard accessible only after login

---

## ⚠️ Known Issues

* Backend must be deployed for full functionality
* CORS must include deployed frontend URL

---

## 🧠 Learnings

* SPA routing issues in production (Vercel)
* CORS configuration in Spring Boot
* Desktop app packaging using Electron
* Deployment workflows (Git → Vercel)

